| casualties1 = 15 killed in action<br>3 missing in action and presumed dead<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pownetwork.org/bios/m/m200.htm|title=Bio, Marshall, Danny G.|website=www.pownetwork.org}}</ref><br/>23 killed en-route in helicopter failure<br>50 wounded<br>3 CH-53 helicopters destroyed
| casualties2 = 13–25 killed in action on Koh Tang<br>unknown killed on Swift Boats and Cambodian mainland<br>15 wounded in action<br>4 Swift Boats sunk
