| title = HM1 Bernard Gause
| work  = The Virtual Wall}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://thewall-usa.com/info.asp?recid=32233
| title = HN Ronald J Manning
| work  = The Virtual Wall}}</ref> and an Air Force crewman<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thewall-usa.com/info.asp?recid=53321
